text: "I'm Your Baby Tonight" was the lead single and title track from Whitney Houston's album of the same name. The song became a major hit for Houston. It reached the Top 10 in many countries. It hit #1 on the U.S. Billboard Hot 100. After her death in 2012, the song was ranked at number 18 by Entertainment Weekly. ==References== Category:1990 songs Category:Pop songs Category:New jack swing songs Category:R&B; songs Category:Whitney Houston songs
